### Index Encryption

All search indexes are encrypted at rest using a multi-layer encryption scheme.

**Encryption Architecture:**

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Layer 1: Operating System Protection                    │
│ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ iOS: Data Protection Class A (Complete Protection)  │ │
│ │ Android: Keystore + File-Based Encryption          │ │
│ └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Layer 2: Application Encryption                         │
│ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ Algorithm: AES-256-GCM                              │ │
│ │ Key Derivation: Argon2id(passkey, salt, 3, 64MB)   │ │
│ │ Key Storage: Secure Enclave / Keystore             │ │
│ └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Layer 3: Segment Encryption                             │
│ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ Each index segment encrypted independently          │ │
│ │ Segment key: HKDF(master_key, segment_id)          │ │
│ │ Compromised segment doesn't expose others          │ │
│ └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Layer 4: Optional PIN/Biometric Gate                    │
│ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ Additional unlock required to access search         │ │
│ │ 3 failed attempts: temporary lockout (5 min)       │ │
│ │ 10 failed attempts: require passkey re-entry       │ │
│ └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Key Management:**

| Key | Derivation | Storage | Rotation |
|-----|------------|---------|----------|
| Master Index Key | Argon2id from passkey | Secure Enclave | On passkey change |
| Segment Keys | HKDF from master | Derived on-demand | Never (immutable segments) |
| Backup Key | Argon2id from passkey + backup salt | Device only | Per backup |
| Sync Key | X25519 key agreement | Per-device keypair | On device deauthorization |

