### Semantic Search

The system supports semantic search that can locate messages based on meaning rather than exact keyword matches. Semantic search utilizes a lightweight on-device embedding model.

**Key Features:**

* Semantic meaning matching beyond keywords
* 100% local processing (no cloud AI)
* Concept-based search ("find travel plans" → vacation, flights, hotels)
* Synonym and paraphrase matching
* Context-aware result ranking
* Related message suggestions
* Search refinement recommendations
* Hybrid keyword + semantic ranking

**On-Device Embedding Model:**

| Property | Specification |
|----------|---------------|
| Model | MiniLM-L6-v2 (quantized INT8) |
| Size | 22 MB |
| Embedding Dimension | 384 |
| Runtime | ONNX Runtime Mobile (iOS/Android) |
| Inference Time | ~50ms per message |
| Languages | English primary, 100+ supported |

