**Semantic Search Limitations:**

| Limitation | Explanation | Mitigation |
|------------|-------------|------------|
| English-optimized | Best performance on English | Keyword fallback for other languages |
| 256 token limit | Long messages truncated | Index first 256 tokens + last 64 |
