## Security Principles

* All search operations are performed locally on the user's device
* Message content is never exposed to external search services
* No search queries are transmitted or logged externally
* Search indexes are encrypted at rest with multiple layers
* Index encryption keys are derived from user passkey, never stored
* Semantic search uses on-device ML model only (22 MB MiniLM)
* Archive data remains fully encrypted with same protections
* Backup data is encrypted client-side before any transmission
* Cross-device sync uses end-to-end encrypted delta protocol
* Shared links include blockchain verification proofs
* User privacy is preserved through local-only processing
* No telemetry, analytics, or usage data leaves the device
* Trust-based filtering protects against low-quality results

## Integration Points

### With Messaging Blueprint

| Feature | Integration |
|---------|-------------|
| Message Receipt | Auto-index on receive, background processing |
| Message Editing | Index original + all edits, search matches any version |
| Message Deletion | Remove from index, tombstone prevents re-index |
| Disappearing Messages | Index until expiry, then purge completely |
| Hidden Folders | Separate encrypted index, biometric required |
| Pinned Messages | `is:pinned` filter, boost in relevance |
| Forwarded Messages | `is:forwarded` filter, track original source |
| Reactions | Index reactions as metadata, `has:reaction` filter |

### With Trust Network Blueprint

| Feature | Integration |
|---------|-------------|
| Trust Levels | `trust:` filter, relevance boosting |
| Trust Circles | `circle:` filter, visibility control |
| Verification | `verified:` filter, badge display in results |
| Blocked Users | Excluded from results, no exceptions |
| Endorsements | `rel:endorsed` filter, ranking boost |
| Privacy Settings | Respect visibility settings in shared links |

### With Silent & Scheduled Blueprint

| Feature | Integration |
|---------|-------------|
| Silent Messages | `is:silent` filter, normal indexing |
| Scheduled Messages | `is:scheduled` for pending, normal after delivery |
| Scheduled Tab | Separate search within scheduled queue |

